  "_provenance": "Every entry is sourced from Internet Archive (archive.org) and carries an explicit Public Domain Mark 1.0 or CC0 license URL on its IA metadata page. The fetch script (audit/fetch_real_corpus.py) verifies the license at download time and refuses to fetch anything whose live licenseurl no longer matches the manifest. PDFs are NOT committed to the repo (audit/cjk-pdfs/.gitignore excludes *.pdf in real/) — fetch on demand.",
